creator: 1RadioNews.com
descriptionHtml:
Podcasts is the quickest way to listen to podcasts you know and love.

Simply search and favorite podcasts.

Then pick an episode and listen.

Nothing complicated!

Discover podcasts by categories as well. News podcasts. Comedy podcasts. Crime podcasts. Podcasts for kids and more.

The Podcasts app is not bloated with features you won't use.

No registration. No tracking. No invasions of privacy. Just the freedom to listen.

The Podcasts app is brought to you by the makers of 1 Radio News, specializing in hourly, daily, and live news headlines, and the TV News app with over 2500 news video channels in 90 languages.
descriptionShort: The simple, quick way to find, follow, and listen to the best podcasts.
